@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}

<div class="jumbotron w3-container w3-center w3-animate-bottom">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome!</h1>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p class="lead">You have found yourself in the online home of W. Ross White and his writing. 
        Enjoy looking around!</p>
    <img class="d-block d-flex justify-content-center img-thumbnail title_image" 
         src="~/images/me_04.jpg" asp-append-version="true" alt="Ross 04 Image Not Found">
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p class="lead">In <a class="hyperlight" asp-area="" asp-page="/AboutRoss/AboutRoss">
        About Ross</a> you can learn about me and what else I get up to, along with information 
        about <a class="hyperlight" asp-area="" asp-page="/AboutRoss/Contact">contacting me</a> and 
        <a class="hyperlight" asp-area="" asp-page="/AboutRoss/Support">supporting me</a>.</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p class="lead">You can explore the original <a class="hyperlight" 
        asp-area="" asp-page="/NewHorizons/About">New Horizons Mission</a> about a generational 
        starship launched a hundred and fifty years from now, to a star a hundred and fifty years 
        away. You can also check out the reboot of Launch which I'm currently working on called 
        <a class="hyperlight" asp-area="" asp-page="/ChasingStars/About.html">Chasing Stars</a>.</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <img class="d-block d-flex justify-content-center img-thumbnail title_image float_right_large" 
         src="~/images/me_05.jpg" alt="Ross 05 Image Not Found">
    <p class="lead">You can also checkout other writings in the Dispatches from the Void. There you 
        can find things like my <a class="hyperlight" 
        href="content/dispatches-from-the-void/updates-blog.html">Updates Blog</a> where I give 
        updates about my writing, and experiences I'd like to share. And don't miss the Just for 
        Fun zone where you can see some of my incredibly cringey early web projects!</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
    <p class="lead">If you are a potential employer in the tech industry who has found your way 
        here while looking me up online, I encourage you to checkout my online resume site as 
        <a href="https://wrosswhite.ca/" class="hyperlight">wrosswhite.ca</a></p>
</div>
